    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Patris et Filii et Spiritus Sancti. Anno Deo propicio pontificatus
                        domni Leonis pape in apostolica sacratissima beati Petri apostoli Domini
                        sede tercio sicq[(ue)] imperante domno Henrico imperatore filius quondam
                        Cohunradi imperatoris in Italia anno quinto, sub anno dominice incarnacionis
                        millesimo quinquagesimo primo, die nona mensis marcii, indictione quarta,
                            <placeName ref="#places/594">RAVENNE</placeName>. Pecii a te quidem in
                        Dei nomine <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Venerandus"
                            >Venerando</name></persName> Dei gratia humili <rs key="#Monks"
                            >monacho</rs>, cum consensu domni <persName
                            key="#Priests #Abbots #Monks" ref="#people/1596">Mainardi</persName>
                        venerabilis <rs key="#Monks">presbiteri</rs> et monachi atque <rs
                            key="#Abbots">abbatis</rs> religiosi <placeName ref="#places/4179"
                            >Pomposiani</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Curtes #Landed_possessions #Forests #Penalty #Cereals #Books #Rent_in_money #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie</orgName> et cum consensu
                        ceterorum servorum Dei ipsius monasterii, UTI mihi presenti in Christi
                        nomine <persName><name ref="Petrus/Porrus">Petro qui vocatur
                            Porrus</name></persName> petitori pro me et <persName><name
                                ref="Christina">Cristina</name></persName> iugali mea in prima parte
                        de rebus inferius dicendis, in secunda et tercia petitor ego ipse pro
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes">Iohanne</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Hugo">Ugone</name></persName> fratribus meis
                        seu filiis nostris, nos omnes filii et nurus quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Tusculus">Tusculi</name></persName>, <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">libelli nomine</rs> concedisti
                        nobis rem iuris suprascripti monasterii, idest <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Size">duodecim t(or)naturias</rs> – duas de
                            <rs key="#Production">terra laboratoria</rs> et decem de <rs
                            key="#Forests">silvis</rs> – que sunt posite in <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >Curte</rs>
                        <geogName
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Confinia #Landed_possessions #Curtes #Forests #Cereals #Penalty #Rent_in_money"
                            ref="#estates/3924"><placeName
                                key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis #Confinia #Landed_possessions #Curtes #Forests #Cereals #Penalty #Rent_in_money"
                                >Anxiata</placeName></geogName>, cum <rs key="#Landed_possessions"
                            >terris</rs>, <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Forests"
                            >silvis</rs> et cum omnibus sibi pertinentibus, sitas <rs key="#Fines"
                            >territorio</rs>
                        <geogName key="#Fines" ref="#estates/2424"><placeName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#places/3513">Fav(entino)</placeName></geogName>, <rs
                            key="#Plebs">plebe</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Plebs" ref="#juridical_persons/1490">Sancti Iohannis qui
                            vocatur in Axiata</orgName>, <rs key="#Confinia">inter affines</rs>
                        eorum: a primo latere <rs key="#Canals">fossato</rs> percurrente, a secundo
                        latere <persName key="#Confinia"><name ref="Ionahhes Varus">Iohannes
                                Varus</name></persName>, a tercio latere <persName key="#Confinia"
                                ><name ref="Ionahhes Punga">Iohannes Punga</name></persName> iure
                        nostro, a quarto quoque latere vos ipsi ordinatores; habendas, tenendas,
                        custodiendas, defensandas et in omnibus meliorandas in annis advenientibus
                        vigintim et novem ad renovandum, sub pensione omni marcii m(ense) infra
                        indictionem <rs key="#Rent_in_money">denarios Venetic(orum) quindecim
                            tantum</rs>. Pro eo quia accepisti c(a)l(ciarium) idest <rs key="#Books"
                            >librum</rs> unum pro <rs key="#Price">denariorum Veneticorum solidos
                            quadraginta</rs>; et vos cum vestris successoribus nobis nostrisque
                        filiis auctoriare debeatis. Si quis vero partis nostre contra hanc
                        peticionem ire temtaverit ante prefinitum tempus quod sup(er) legitur det
                        pars parti fidem servanti, ANTE [omne lit]is inicium aut interpellacionem,
                        pene nomine <rs key="#Penalty">auri uncias duas</rs> et post pene solucione
                        maneat hec peticio in sua firmitate. QUAM vero peticionem UUIDONE(m) Dei
                        misericordia tabellionem Ravennatem scribendum rogavi, sub die menseque et
                        anno atque indictione suprascripta quarta, RAVENNE. + Signum + manus Petri
                        qui vocatur Porrus iamdicti petitoris ad omnia que sup(er) legitur.</ab>
